"more.title" = "More";
"general.title" = "About the festival";
"general.content" = "Roots, folk and world music between tradition and avant-garde, dancefloor-feeling and cosy garden concerts – all this offers „one of the finest music festivals on the planet“ (fRoots Great Britain)

For its 34th edition, the festival welcomes Austria as the special guest country. Alongside Viennese songs, Austropop, Alpine traditions and contemporary folk sounds, the program once again includes cinema, exhibitions, the RUTH award, children’s dances and street music.";
"general.extra.title" = "Please note!";
"general.extra.content" = "Tickets for the Rudolstadt Festival are only available in advance. The same applies to the combination tickets with overnight stay at one of the campsites, as well as the parking tickets. At the box office you only get day tickets for the festival area downtown.";
